{"tid":1569390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"榮光連台語版都有埋，而且係可以照唱嘅！","createTime":"2019-09-14T15:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T01:40:29.000Z","uid":74155,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"531c136004a1d9e5026faa667cb3c8807f29860c","tid":1569390,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:06:44.000Z","msg":"為何這土地目屎流<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">uī-h&ocirc; che th&oacute;͘-tē ba̍k-s&aacute;i l&acirc;u</span><br />\n為何予眾人攏憤恨<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">uī-h&ocirc; hō͘  ch&egrave;ng-l&acirc;ng l&ocirc;ng h&uacute;n-hīn</span><br />\n攑頭勿恬恬喝拂聲響透<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">gia̍h-th&acirc;u m&agrave;i tiām-tiām hoah-hut siaⁿ hi&uacute;ⁿ th&agrave;u</span><br />\n望自由歸佇香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">bāng chū-i&ucirc; kui-tī hiang-k&aacute;ng</span><br />\n<br />\n為何這驚惶趕袂走<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">uī-h&ocirc; che kiaⁿ-hi&acirc;ⁿ ku&aacute;ⁿ beh ch&aacute;u</span><br />\n為何為信念毋捌退後<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">uī-h&ocirc; uī s&igrave;n-liām m̄-bat th&egrave;-āu</span><br />\n因何血咧流前進聲猶響透<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">in-h&ocirc; hueh teh l&acirc;u chi&acirc;n-ch&igrave;n siaⁿ i&aacute;u hi&uacute;ⁿ th&agrave;u</span><br />\n建自由光輝香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">ki&agrave;n chū-i&ucirc; kong-hui hiang-k&aacute;ng</span><br />\n<br />\n咧暗星墜落徬徨暝半<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">teh &agrave;m-sing tuī-lo̍h p&oacute;ng-h&ocirc;ng m&icirc;-p&ograve;aⁿ</span><br />\n迷霧內對遠方吹來號筒聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">b&ecirc;-bū lāi u&igrave; &oacute;an-hong chhoe l&acirc;i hō-t&acirc;ng siaⁿ</span><br />\n保自由來齊集佇遮來全力對敵<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">p&oacute; chū-i&ucirc; l&acirc;i ch&ecirc;-chi̍p tī-chia l&acirc;i ch&ocirc;an-le̍k t&ugrave;i-te̍k</span><br />\n勇氣智慧永遠不滅<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">i&oacute;ng-kh&igrave; t&igrave;-hūi &eacute;ng-&oacute;an put-bia̍t</span><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到愛光復這香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">l&ecirc;-b&ecirc;ng l&acirc;i-k&agrave;u &agrave;i kong-ho̍k che hiang-k&aacute;ng</span><br />\n男女鬥陣為正義時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">l&acirc;m-l&uacute; t&agrave;u-tīn uī ch&egrave;ng-gī s&icirc;-tāi kek-bēng</span><br />\n祈求民主佮自由萬世永不朽<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">k&icirc;-ki&ucirc; b&icirc;n-ch&uacute; kah chū-i&ucirc; bān-s&egrave; &eacute;ng put-hi&uacute;</span><br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">g&oacute;a gōan &ecirc;ng-kng kui hiang-k&aacute;ng</span><br />\n<br />\n注︰<br />\n予=令，使<br />\n攏=亦，都<br />\n勿=唔，唔好，咪<br />\n佇=於，喺<br />\n袂=唔，唔得<br />\n毋捌=唔識<br />\n咧=在<br />\n對=由<br />\n遮=此，呢度<br />\n愛=要<br />\n佮=與，及，同"},{"pid":"d6ace7279e3a71d120eec4824892ed6146e24820","tid":1569390,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8d9090d46f7aca52938df85d02e80f116541ab","tid":1569390,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e066757a55c879bf346fce68341c7add261ad5","tid":1569390,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3712a14ab707b35155c63d809eed02b21a83f821","tid":1569390,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"27230ab5cfc07dcfffb8df7242659bfbec309d04","tid":1569390,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3712a14ab707b35155c63d809eed02b21a83f821","tid":1569390,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:15:33.000Z","msg":"一講到語言話題，永遠得你撐場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇來連登真係少語言撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji